      <section>
         <title>Testing</title>
         <ul>
            <li>Test data: we are marking up gold-standard documents with a relatively simple, plain-text <a
            href="spelling/testdoc/error-markup.html">error markup</a>.</li>
            <li>The test data is converted to xml and is stored in
            <code>$GTFREE/stable/goldstandard/converted/</code></li>
            <li>You run a speller test using the following command: <code>make GTLANG=sma TESTTOOL=pl
            correct-test</code></li>
            <li>We also have a <a href="spelling/testdoc/PLXConversionTesting.html">plan for creating Unit Tests for the
            PLX conversion</a> used to build our MS Office tools</li>
            <li>Technical release testing for <a href="admin/Divvun2.2ReleaseTesting.html">Divvun 2.2</a></li>
         </ul>
      </section>
